Have been here a few times and they never disappoint! Such amazing food and service. The staff is very friendly, family owned. The place is immaculate and very clean. The decor is wonderful. It's hard to find a good Thai place as clean as this. The food is wonderful too. Lunch specials is a great price ranging from $8-$12. They have a soup of the day that's always amazing. I love their coconut ice cream also. I always want to go to this place when in the area and hungry for Thai food! It's always busy when I come in. Don't be angry if the staff isn't that attentive they are just busy but very nice people! Love this place and love Thai food.

