I love this place and especially the fact that their kitchen is open until 2am!! The crab puffs are super yummy I get them every time I'm here. The decor is unique for a Chinese restaurant and I love it. The owners are awesome too! One is always behind the bar and he's really friendly. Thursday nights are stand up comedy and it's great.

