I really enjoy living at the glen it's the perfect location and the pricing is great. Electricity is inexpensive every month even though we keep our apartment at 65 everyday! The updated clubhouse is really nice and so are the pools (there are multiple pools). The apartments are nice and clean. I can't wait to upgrade to Visconti at the end of our lease! I would recommend this complex you just can't beat the price and location! Perfect for students attending Scottsdale community college or even ASU. also it's close to everything you need and many job opportunities in this area.

